</style><h2 id="outline__4" class="wp-block-heading">胡拉·阮</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHcy3pebkDp_2b14SPAcpFyhb6UpLLjuTMTVL0iZXtfWf83l9rWqc2DWU7y3QQklkAyScIqhDXpwD-fHgsKrKnVqTyUfIM9KAf-cvRwiKlUiv8jBbDrZ8EvQOF3xyGJIsiqll61h3yQ_MB12XKdtfitQ=w1097-h740-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2023 Horipro Inc.</figcaption></figure><p>擅长伪装术，以怪盗为生。</p><p>当他潜入某宅邸时，被巡逻的管家抓住，但他天生友善的性格，与宅邸中的每个人都成为了朋友，并经常出入宅邸。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="我收到了怪盗【Horaku Luan】的通知“#New Vtuber”" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zUK1G-T8Lng?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td> YouTube 官方频道</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Houra_Ruan" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="胡拉·阮 [Nextopia]">胡拉·阮 [Nextopia]</a></td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）官方账号</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/HouraRuan" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="霍乐栾🃏💎">霍乐栾<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f0cf.png" alt="🃏" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f48e.png" alt="💎" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a></td></tr><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>科科卡纳 (@cocokana_ovo)</td></tr><tr><td>实时二维设计</td><td>小丸江藤 (@KoDa_mat)</td></tr><tr><td>预定首发发行日期</td><td>2023年（令和5年）11月24日 19:30~</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__5" class="wp-block-heading">尼科尼科·波纳</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHfHdqs-YNkKrER5N